      "categories": ["grouped", "alternation", "quantified", "open-ended-repeat", "conditional", "group-exists", "optional-group", "compile", "metadata", "str", "gap"],
      "notes": [
        "Publishes the numbered compile frontier for one optional grouped open-ended `{1,}` alternation followed by one later group-exists conditional without widening into replacements, backreferences, nested grouped conditionals, or broader grouped backtracking."
